AMINOACID_STATES

public static final int[] AMINOACID_STATES
This table maps amino acid characters into state codes (0-25). Amino Acids go ACDEFGHIKLMNPQRSTVWYBZX*?-, Other letters; j, o, and u are mapped to ? *, ? and - are mapped to themselves All other chars are mapped to -
